item.title: Stars
item.description: Awoke and looked at the starts in the night. Eyes may be more relaxed and sensitive at that time. Also I assume they may move slower and movements may be less calibrated. Some stars are clear, some are twinkling, and other are faint. While clear stars make a space with landmarks. Through twinkling one comes to faint and they are the interesting ones. They are both fish and water of the night sky.
